node.text: Chionesu Bakari is a mentorship organization that just celebrated serving over 500 young Black men in NYC for the past 15 years. I got the pleasure of congratulating a group of high school seniors from the program. Thanks to @americaneagle, I hooked the guys up with some fits that will have them not only looking their best but feeling their best stepping into this next chapter. Check out @cbyoungmen to learn more about the amazing work this organization is doing. #chionesubakari #aepartner
